---
title: Slow-Cooked Beef Gravy & Veggie Casserole with Potato Mash & Parsley
description: Here’s a dish that will teleport you back in time - a beef casserole. Slow-cooked in rosemary and spice this casserole will be devoured in no time. Complete the taste of nostalgia with a buttery mash and a variety of veggies for a dinner that might even rival Nanna’s!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
